Package View_Controller

Class ScreenChange

  • java.lang.Object
    • View_Controller.ScreenChange
  • public class ScreenChange
extends java.lang.Object
    Screen change class which helps to change scenes throughout the application. This class helps in eliminating a tremendous amount of duplicate code throughout by allowing the methods within to be called to navigate to different screens.
